      "content": "that's a good start. can you expand on the \"appearance\" part though? like, if i'm writing about being \"polished\" and \"sophisticated,\" what are the actual standard clothing items or styles that everyone should aim for to look professional? i want to give readers a clear blueprint of what a \"globally sophisticated\" look really is.",
